name: Sophia Lindqvist Painter May 10, 2021
description: is a Swedish/New York based artist. She is a painter, with a special interest for the human figure and the relationship between the world of humans and the natural world. Her art has been the subject of several publications and exhibitions. She is represented by Gallery Hubert in Stockholm and One and JG Gallery in New York. She has been using NFTs to curate artwork since 2016. https://www.instagram.com/evartology/
